catalyst: The catalyst used in the experiment is Ir-ppy (Iridium(III) 2-phenylpyridine complex) combined with NAHN-Tp COF (Covalent Organic Framework).
light source: The light source used in the experiment is a 300 W Xe lamp with a cut-off filter (k 420 nm).
lamp: The lamp used in the experiment is a 300 W Xe lamp.
reaction medium: The reaction medium used in the experiment is a mixture of MeCN/TEOA (6 mL, 5:1, v/v).
